Image Prompt:
Create an ethereal and serene depiction of Jesus being baptized in the Jordan River. The scene should feature a peaceful river with gentle ripples, surrounded by lush greenery. Show Jesus standing waist-deep in the water, with rays of heavenly light shining down upon him. Capture the moment of baptism with a dove symbolizing the Holy Spirit descending from above. Emphasize the sacredness and spiritual significance of this biblical event through a harmonious blend of natural elements and divine illumination.
